snippet.title: New Updates On Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Ongoing Trial
snippet.description:
In today’s video we are going to talk about the ongoing trial between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard aka the Libel Trial.  

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

It has created a lot of controversy and while some have sympathized with Heard, other have taken Johnny’s side because the evidence points otherwise and well, we too believe that whatever is going between the two must come to a resolute end now.
